        private static AccessPointNode select​(java.util.List<Node> nodes,
                                      WiFi_network_MAS.Strategy str)
        Strategy to decide the access point: Random Selector = The AP gets chosen as a random node RSSI Selector = The AP gets voted by the nodes depending on the RSSI; The AP with the highest amount of votes becomes the new access point.
        Parameters:
        nodes - the list of nodes on which the selection must be run
        str - the chosen strategy
        Returns:
        AccessPointNode the chosen AP node
